'From Squeak3.2gamma of 17 January 2002 [latest update: #4889] on 23 June 2002 at 1:36:02 pm'!"Change Set:		resourceColorFixDate:			23 June 2002Author:			Bob ArningWhen loading resource Forms, do NOT discard color table information. It was only with the advent of update 4878 that this became an issue."!!Form methodsFor: 'resources' stamp: 'RAA 6/23/2002 13:34'!readNativeResourceFrom: byteStream	| img aStream |	(byteStream isKindOf: FileStream) ifTrue:[		"Ugly, but ImageReadWriter will send #reset which is implemented as #reopen and we may not be able to do so."		aStream _ RWBinaryOrTextStream with: byteStream contents.	] ifFalse:[		aStream _ byteStream.	].	img _ [ImageReadWriter formFromStream: aStream] on: Error do:[:ex| nil].	img ifNil:[^nil].	img displayOn: self.	img _ nil.! !